sections.heading: funds of a prepaid limited health service organization shall be invested only in cash, certificates of deposit, or obligations of a state or of the United States

sections.text:
44-4715.Investments.

The funds of a prepaid limited health service organization shall be invested only in cash, certificates of deposit, or obligations of a state or of the United States.

SourceLaws 1989, LB 320, ยง 15.
